    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require outdoor venues to ban dog access in extreme hot weather",
        "additional_details": "So many people don\u2019t understand the risk of walking dogs in extreme heat. It\u2019s hard to educate everyone however if venues banned dog access when the temperature is too high, less dogs would face the heatstroke, suffering and potential death caused by overheating.",
        "background": "Require all outside event venues to ban dog access when the weather is considered too hot and dangerous for dogs.",
